text: Maaqo inkih israa-iil xayloh calaalih Sugte israa-iil (Nabii Yaq-qhuvb kinnuk) isi nafsil carammoyse maaqo akke waytek, tawraat kitab obsimak naharat, Nabiyow keenik ixxic:tawraat kitab Baahaay kay Addal tanim Akriya, Nabii yaq-qhuub isi nafsil carammoysem Yalli tawraat Addal oobise iyyaanamal Numma yacee mara tekkeenik, Qhuraan Addal israa-iil xaylol tawraat oobak duma Yalli tu-carammoyse weem taaxigeenimkeh, Nabii Yaq-qhuub isi nafsil carammoysem Akke waytek
